ubx_message.description: This message reports the precise GLO time of the most recent navigation solution including validity flags and an accuracy estimate.

fields.name: iTOW
fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch. See section iTOW timestamps in the integration manual for details.

fields.name: TOD
fields.description: GLONASS time of day (rounded to integer seconds)

fields.name: fTOD
fields.description: Fractional part of TOD (range: +/-500000000). The precise GLONASS time of day in seconds is: TOD + fTOD * 1e-9

fields.name: Nt
fields.description: Current date (range: 1-1461), starting at 1 from the 1st Jan of the year indicated by N4 and ending at 1461 at the 31st Dec of the third year after that indicated by N4

fields.name: N4
fields.description: Four-year interval number starting from 1996 (1=1996, 2=2000, 3=2004...)

fields.name: valid
fields.description: Validity flags

bit_fields.name: todValid
bit_fields.description: 1 = Valid TOD and fTOD (see section Time validity in the integration manual for details)

bit_fields.name: dateValid
bit_fields.description: 1 = Valid N4 and Nt (see section Time validity in the integration manual for details)

fields.name: tAcc
fields.description: Time Accuracy Estimate
